CopyArrivalDate yes
SyncState *
Create Both
Expunge Both

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User roland.puntaier@gmail.com
PassCmd "pass gmail/roland.puntaier@gmail.com"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/.local/var/mail/gmail/
Inbox ~/.local/var/mail/gmail/INBOX

Channel gmail-default
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns INBOX

Channel gmail-drafts
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :gmail-local:Drafts
Create Slave

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:Sent
Create Slave

Channel gmail-starred
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Starred"
Slave :gmail-local:Starred
Create Slave

Channel gmail-important
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Important"
Slave :gmail-local:Important
Create Slave

Channel gmail-spam
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Spam"
Slave :gmail-local:Spam
Create Slave

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Trash"
Slave :gmail-local:Trash
Create Slave

Group gmail
Channel gmail-default
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-sent
Channel gmail-starred
Channel gmail-important
Channel gmail-spam
Channel gmail-trash

